l/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b84086e2c961df4e807dde6a19b049944e78ff3b","tid":298351,"uid":59839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T10:24:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>貓唔撚鍾意出街的</blockquote><br />\n弱智主人話佢地會出就要出</blockquote><br />\n我隻貓一帶佢出去睇醫生就驚到粒肉球流哂汗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  仲話帶佢出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92cc9d049cf7cd1ffb1b7c617406f3efdb3038d0","tid":298351,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T10:28:18.000Z","msg":"咩叫開綠燈"},{"pid":"6c45e8abf2265d4b4da5dffc85e9f1b832f7d6df","tid":298351,"uid":34410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T10:31:45.000Z","msg":"實成架車都係狗屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65e3b7880d576856341c7b44c8c45ab98cd3dca5","tid":298351,"uid":9542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T10:35:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>貓唔撚鍾意出街的</blockquote><br />\n弱智主人話佢地會出就要出</blockquote><br />\n我隻貓一帶佢出去睇醫生就驚到粒肉球流哂汗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  仲話帶佢出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n驚到叫到仆街先係問題所在，無車都係搭返的士算"},{"pid":"c567d77dd7e3c1f775cc2108afe5ba1894116762","tid":298351,"uid":26067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T10:36:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 蛇，變色龍，雀都係某種人嘅寵物<